text: The Wondermints are an American rock band. They are from Los Angeles.They released four studio albums between 1995 and 2002. They are also known for serving as part of the backing band for Brian Wilson since 1999.also known for serving as part of the backing band for Brian Wilson since 1999. They were formed in 1992, and released a vinyl single, "Proto Pretty", which was later compiled on Rhino Records' "Poptopia" series of power pop compilations.
